{"data":[{"id":561741973,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561741973","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545995189,"updated_time":1545995189,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e今天上高代课的时候，高代老师讲的一个事例可以送给提问者\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e大概在零几年的时候，有一个学长一入学就表示出了对此类问题的极高兴趣，然后就整天只研究数论方面的的问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而且还说他证出来了让老师看是否正确，但老师说那只有一页纸的证明，他是看都不会看的，如果这么简单的话，那前面那么多大数学家是傻子吗？最后好像那位学长挂了许多专业课，并没有毕业。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e每年都有许多人声称自己证出了哥德巴赫猜想这类的，但是都是沉浸在自己的世界中不可自拔。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你还是个高中生，那我想说你的路还长，如果你真心喜爱数学，欢迎你报考数学专业，从最基础的数分高代学起，那你会了解到原来高中的数学知识不值一提。只有你不断向上攀登，你才能看到更加广阔的世界，而并不是现在山下看着山峰说：“这不是触手可及吗？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还有清华北大到底对你意味着什么，是旁人提起的无限荣耀还是虚荣或者自身能力的肯定，那样的你并不适合专心于数学研究。清华北大只能意味着你有更好的教育平台，但是你的成就也只能由你来一步一步的完成，如果你真的喜爱数学，我相信就算是一个二本的大学也并不会阻止你进步的脚步。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不要过分在意别人的冷嘲热讽，人不轻狂枉少年，但是当下的你就是属于忍受不了正派的扎马步打基本功然后选择了走火入魔的一派人。你更应该做到的是提升自己的眼界和能力，17岁的你做不到，也许70岁的你就能做到呢？\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"今天上高代课的时候，高代老师讲的一个事例可以送给提问者大概在零几年的时候，有一个学长一入学就表示出了对此类问题的极高兴趣，然后就整天只研究数论方面的的问题。而且还说他证出来了让老师看是否正确，但老师说那只有一页纸的证明，他是看都不会看的，…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1014\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author